  "prompt": "What % of stories in Quora would be real?",
  "response": "Estimating the percentage of real versus fictional stories on Quora is challenging, as the platform allows users to share personal experiences, opinions, and fictional narratives. While many users provide genuine accounts, there are also fictional stories, exaggerations, or anecdotes that may not reflect reality. \n\nIt\u2019s difficult to provide a specific percentage, as this can vary widely by topic, individual users, and the nature of the question being asked. For a more accurate understanding, one would need to analyze a representative sample of stories on the platform. It's essential for readers to critically assess the credibility of individual stories and consider the context in which they are shared.",
